messages.title: Putting local people first
messages.content: Tessa has worked tirelessly and made a real difference 'Tessa has been there for us all the way through the founding of the Elmgreen School. She has worked tirelessly behind the scenes, has a passion for life, and has made a real difference in our community.' Sandy Nuttgens, Parent Promoters Foundation Chair - pictured with Tessa at the opening of one of the five new schools delivered locally
